# Folder ini menyimpan hasil training (dipisah per jenis model):
#
# model/chatbot/    -> chatbot Qwen 2.5 + LoRA (training_model.py)
#     lora_adapter/ -> adapter LoRA (ringan, butuh base model)
#     merged/       -> model gabungan siap pakai (jika training pakai --merge)
#     checkpoints/  -> checkpoint selama training
#
# model/lstm/       -> model LSTM cuaca per variabel (training_lstm.py)
#     lstm_<target>.pt, lstm_scalers_<target>.joblib, lstm_pred_<target>.png
#
# model/word2vec/   -> model Word2Vec (training_word_vector.py)
#     word2vec.model
